---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Weekend Hobbyist — Your Starting Path | Flight School Friend"
  description="You may fit a flexible local PPL path focused on fun, skill-building, and sustainable weekly training. Here's your recommended roadmap."
>
  <section class="bg-white max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs font-bold rounded-full mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Your Recommended Path</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-6">Weekend Hobbyist</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-4 font-medium">You're likely a good fit for a flexible PPL path.</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">This is a starting recommendation, not a final training decision.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Roadmap Timeline -->
    <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12">
      <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm border-b border-slate-200 pb-2">Roadmap Timeline</h3>
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 items-start md:items-center text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">
        <div class="bg-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 shadow-sm whitespace-nowrap">Discovery Flight</div>
        <span class="hidden md:inline text-slate-300">&rarr;</span>
        <div class="bg-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 shadow-sm whitespace-nowrap">Medical / Student Cert</div>
        <span class="hidden md:inline text-slate-300">&rarr;</span>
        <div class="bg-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 shadow-sm whitespace-nowrap">Choose Part 61/Club</div>
        <span class="hidden md:inline text-slate-300">&rarr;</span>
        <div class="bg-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 shadow-sm whitespace-nowrap">Train 1–2x Weekly</div>
        <span class="hidden md:inline text-slate-300">&rarr;</span>
        <div class="bg-sky-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg shadow-sm whitespace-nowrap">PPL</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Why / Clarify -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Why this fits:</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-600">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-bold">✓</span> You are likely interested in flying for fun, personal growth, or local trips.</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-bold">✓</span> You may not need an accelerated career-style program.</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-bold">✓</span> Flexibility, instructor fit, and sustainable weekly training may matter more than speed.</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-bold">✓</span> A local Part 61 school or flying club may be worth comparing.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">What to clarify next:</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-600">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-amber-500 font-bold">?</span> Can you train at least 1–2 times per week?</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-amber-500 font-bold">?</span> What is your realistic monthly training budget?</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-amber-500 font-bold">?</span> Do you want to rent, join a club, or eventually own?</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-amber-500 font-bold">?</span> Are there medical or scheduling issues to solve first?</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Email CTA -->
    <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl mb-16 text-center">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Email me my PPL starter roadmap</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6">Get this checklist and next steps sent directly to your inbox.</p>
      <form id="email-form" class="max-w-md mx-auto flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2">
        <input type="email" placeholder="Your email address" required class="flex-grow px-4 py-3 rounded-lg text-slate-900 outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sky-500" />
        <button type="submit" class="px-6 py-3 bg-sky-600 hover:bg-sky-500 font-bold rounded-lg transition">Send Roadmap</button>
      </form>
      <p id="email-success" class="hidden text-green-400 font-medium mt-4">Got it — your roadmap would be sent here in the live version.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Related Resources -->
    <div class="mb-12 border-t border-slate-200 pt-12">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Related Resources</h3>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/guides/flight-school-cost/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition">Flight School Cost Guide</a>
        <a href="/guides/part-61-vs-part-141/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition">Part 61 vs Part 141</a>
        <a href="/guides/how-to-choose-a-flight-school/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition">How to Choose a Flight School</a>
        <a href="/guides/private-pilot-requirements/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition">Private Pilot Requirements</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center">
      <a href="/flight-school-decision-tool/quiz/" class="text-sky-600 font-medium hover:underline flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"></path></svg>
        Retake the Quiz
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
  document.getElementById('email-form')?.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    (e.target as HTMLElement).classList.add('hidden');
    document.getElementById('email-success')?.classList.remove('hidden');
  });
</script>
